Package opennlp.ccg.hylo.graph Description

Provides representations of LFs as traversible graphs based on the JGraphT package, as well as customized filters for sets of edges in those graphs.

LFGraphs can be created on their own, or from an existing LF (or XML structure representing one) using the LFGraphFactory. LF graphs are also customizable in that different edge factories can be specified by implementing LFEdgeFactory (a default implementation is provided in DefaultLFEdgeFactory).
